title: Project Blue Beam
cleaned_text:
If you are a Believer in Jesus Christ and His Rapture of the Church, this particular page may be of the utmost importance to you.

Project Blue Beam deals primarily with Hologram Technology. This is something we are going to see more and more of. The Globalists have already started to introduce this technology to us to get us used to it. In fact, it was most recently "used" during the November 2008 elections. I put "used" in quotes, because I am using the term lightly. They wanted you to believe it was really a Hologram that they were using, but in reality it was just a glorified special effect.

So what's this all about? Let's get started... CLICK HERE to watch more videos on Project Blue Beam CLICK HERE to read more about Project Blue Beam
